name: LGBTQIA+ Combo
description: Some events are so so so so important that we NEED to speak about them! And LGBTQIA+ Pride Month is one of this! We have here a vegetarian burger (chickpea burger) with onions, pickles, tomatoes, mushrooms and our special mayo with herbs; a coke; fries and Macarons for dessert!!! More than a combo, this one is a symbol of fight for freedom and for equality! It's a symbol of Respect and Love! It's a symbol of humanity! If you wanna buy it, call me on twitter @Criptoburguer Note: HLE= "Happiness level after eat it"
